{"tid":336611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又係支那製]香港機場新捷運系統合同授予浦鎮龐巴迪-中車浦鎮聯合體","createTime":"2017-07-26T14:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T01:13:18.000Z","uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0936bd247eb45f19335d57fa593f6027313b09a","tid":336611,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T14:36:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hongkongairport.com/eng/business/airport-authority/business-opportunities/1497404277539.html?notice-of-contract-award\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongairport.com%2Feng%2Fbusiness%2Fairport-authority%2Fbusiness-opportunities%2F1497404277539.html%3Fnotice-of-contract-award&d=WsCSeNEfer1iRA6tRQe%2FWMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=7bcdc1a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongairport.com/eng/business/airport-authority/business-opportunities/1497404277539.html?notice-of-contract-award</a><br />\nNotice of Contract Award &ndash; New Automated People Mover System (TRC Line) (Contract 3601)<br />\nNotice is hereby given that the Airport Authority of HKIA Tower, 1 Sky Plaza Road, Hong Kong International Airport, Lantau, Hong Kong awarded Contract 3601 for New Automated People Mover System (TRC Line) at the Hong Kong International Airport to CRRC Puzhen Bombardier Transportation Systems Limited and CRRC Nanjing Puzhen Co., Ltd. of 8/F., Unit 2, Building 11, Mingfa Jiangsu Park, No. 5 North Pudong Road, Pukou, Nanjing, People&rsquo;s Republic of China on 13 June 2017. The awarded sum was HK$1,668,324,457.<br />\n<br />\nThis procurement was conducted by open tender. An invitation to tender for this Contract was published on the Airport Authority&rsquo;s website (<a href=\"http://www.hkairport.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkairport.com&d=WsCSeNEfer1iRA6tRQe%2FWMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=50d260de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.hkairport.com</a>) on 28th November 2016."},{"pid":"4458a6f5c4be2bd464